=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenge</h2><br>Help Elena care for her grandmother by collecting memories! You have to overcome intense and unique challenges to collect these memories from mysterious places located in the past!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790880/extras/a039dff1a765d66d81d5bdab4c9f8d80.poster.avif?t=1635780932\" width=514 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790880/extras/a039dff1a765d66d81d5bdab4c9f8d80.webm?t=1635780932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790880/extras/a039dff1a765d66d81d5bdab4c9f8d80.mp4?t=1635780932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
